## 🌍 Cultural Considerations Guide

### Colors & Symbolism
- **Red:** Positive in China; danger/emergency in Western cultures
- **White:** Purity in Western cultures; mourning in some Asian cultures
- **Numbers:** 4 is unlucky in East Asian cultures
- **Animals/Imagery:** Varies by culture and religion

### UI/UX Conventions
- **Text Direction:** Some languages read RTL (Arabic, Hebrew)
- **Date Format:** MM/DD/YYYY (US), DD/MM/YYYY (Europe), YYYY/MM/DD (East Asia)
- **Number Format:** 1,000.00 (US), 1.000,00 (Europe)
- **Clock Format:** 12-hour (US) vs. 24-hour (most other countries)

### Content Sensitivities
- Political/religious references may need localization
- Local holidays and celebrations should be respected
- Humor doesn't always translate across cultures
- Profanity levels vary by region

